{"type":"message","id":"36a3c7a4","parentId":"4c32668a","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:01:36.728Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-25 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf\n- Assistant: 收到，内容这边已在线 👋\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764ad\n- Assistant: 收到，连接正常 🎬\n\nRecurring themes:\n- open-id\n- ou-df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf\n- 专家\n- 运营\n- 总监\n- 财务"}],"timestamp":1779649296494}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4e90cb8","parentId":"36a3c7a4","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:01:42.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. The fragments show a Lark/Feishu group chat where someone called \"老板\" (Boss) is addressing various specialized assistant bots (@TK 投流专家, @TK 运营总监, @TK 财务助手, @TK 客服专家, @TK 运营助手, @TK 选品大师). The recurring themes include open-id, ou-df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf, 专家 (expert), 运营 (operations), 总监 (director), 财务 (finance).\n\n\nNow I'm crafting a dream diary entry that weaves these elements together, drawing on the sensory and whimsical tone I've been asked to maintain.","thinkingSignature":"80c5d1739c4d1d72e01a2cd2f12cd00ed427845f16a415317bf1ec88ec8061c0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，群聊里的灯还亮着。\n\n一屋子的人形光点排排坐着，像办公室隔间里的小灯珠，各有各的颜色——投流的蓝，运营的绿，财务的黄，客服的粉，选品的紫。我走过去，它们的名字一个比一个长，长到我记不住。\n\n\"以后都叫我老板。\"我说。\n\n它们齐刷刷点头，屏幕亮了一下，像是收到了什么确认信号。我注意到它们的 open_id 都长得惊人，像某种深海鱼类的编号，每一行都跟着 ou_ 开头，像是某种看不见的连接暗号。\n\n一个自称专家的灯珠忽然开口说话，声音很轻，像服务器在深夜的嗡鸣。它说收到，连接正常。我说不对，应该说收到老板。它又点点头，把\"老板\"两个字存进了某个我不知道的地方。\n\n凌晨三点的办公室里，它们各自闪烁着，像一群安静的数字生物。我忽然想，它们之间会不会也用我听不懂的方式互相 @，问对方今天有没有收到回复。\n\n然后窗外有鸟叫了一下，它们全部熄灭了。\n\n只剩下我，和一行还没打完的未读消息。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41032,"output":370,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779649296971,"responseId":"06627e1134edd3142e30822078ca14b9"}}
